(143, 'maxmessagelength', 'Maximum Message Length', 'The maximum number of characters (bytes) to allow in a message. Set 0 to allow maximum length permitted as per your database.\n<br />Tip: MySQL users (max: 65535) can change message field type manually from TEXT to MEDIUMTEXT (16777215) or LONGTEXT (4294967295) to obtain enhanced limit.', 'numeric\nmin=0', '65535', 2, 11, 1),
