(147, 'postmergemins', 'Post Merge Time', 'With this enabled, posts posted within x minutes by the same author right after each other, will be merged. Set the time limit (in minutes) to merge posts. Set to 0 to disable this feature. Default: 60', 'numeric\nmin=0', '60', 6, 11, 1),
