(157, 'maxquotedepth', 'Maximum Nested Quote Tags', 'The maximum depth level for quote tags. When quote-replying to a post, all nested quotes which exceed this threshold are automatically removed. Note that this value is only enforced when quote-replying - it is still possible to manually enter quotes to exceed this limit, and this setting will not affect posts already submitted. Set to 0 to disable.', 'numeric\nmin=0', '5', 16, 11, 1),
